<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فيها قتل قليج <span class="c2">(بن)</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span> أرسلان <span class="c2">(صاحب الروم)</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
